      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This exceptional vehicle represents the absolute pinnacle of automotive preservation. Maintained to an exacting standard, the exterior retains its original showroom luster, while the cabin remains entirely free of wear or imperfection. Every mechanical system has been rigorously vetted to ensure performance that mirrors its factory-delivered state. For the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this offering presents a rare opportunity to acquire a truly pristine specimen of the marque.",
