    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home. This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014it seriously looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It has been totally babied, kept in a climate-controlled garage, and drives like an absolute dream. You won't find a single scratch or hiccup here. If you're looking for total perfection, this is the one! Feel free to reach out if you want to come see it in person!",
      "price": 43500.0,
