    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD, showcasing a meticulously preserved 13B-REW power plant. This specimen features a factory-spec sequential twin-turbocharger configuration with a definitive boost transition and zero oil blow-by. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp five-speed manual transmission and a Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque vectoring. The chassis maintains its original structural rigidity, complemented by aluminum double-wishbone suspension components that remain free of bushing fatigue. Recent service includes a comprehensive cooling system overhaul and a verified compression test with exceptional PSI readings across all rotor faces. This is a rare, thermally-optimized example of a front-midship icon, free of typical vacuum line degradation or synchro wear.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
