    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that stands as a testament to meticulous ownership. This car is in showroom condition, having been stored exclusively in a climate-controlled garage and never driven in inclement weather. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating with absolutely no chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any bolster wear or creasing, and it still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every feature, from the panoramic sunroof to the advanced infotainment suite and ambient lighting, operates with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It has been serviced ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, with a complete, documented history included in the sale. The engine bay is detailed and spotless, and the undercarriage shows no signs of road debris or oxidation. This sale includes two sets of keys, the original window sticker, and all owner\u2019s manuals. For the buyer seeking a vehicle that is indistinguishable from new, this is the definitive choice.",
